Example mediation data

Source: R/data-example250.R
example250.Rd

This data was randomly generated and based off the example data provided in the SAS macro <https://www.hsph.harvard.edu/tyler-vanderweele/tools-and-tutorials/>

example250

Format

A data table with 250 rows and 6 variables:

id

Numeric identifier for each observation (1:250)

x

Random binary variable (0,1)

m

Random binary variable (0,1)

y

Random continuous variable (-3.04 to 3.54)

cens

Random binary variable (0,1)

c

Random continuous variable (-3.11 to 2.52)
